{"tid":1493014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸為咗同美國對抗, 連香港爆頭警司都要吹奏","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:36:43.000Z","uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25d72811676309f2879680053ae580e669d5bd70","tid":1493014,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"一路繼續吹香港警察有幾好<br />\n一路整啲美國有幾差<br />\n<br />\n真心, 大陸咁鍾意班香港警察, 黑警你地番大陸生活啦不如, 上去讀書, 上去睇醫生, 上去食大陸野, 中國人咁支持你地可能全部免費呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於大陸仔, 你地咁憎美國, 就咪去美國生活, 唔好用美國貨, 你地所有既日常用品都有大陸品牌, 唔好用外國貨, 迪士尼都唔好去呀<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇美國人劉亦菲套美國迪士尼作品<br />\n花木蘭, 你地睇係送緊錢比美國人咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSnD6Mt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSnD6Mt.png&h=ac87aa41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tywadru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTywadru.png&h=08847f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9oebHjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9oebHjQ.png&h=61c5838e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7doyry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7doyry.png&h=01f1bb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89298790baba8cce30add1ea52b9af7cbd353895","tid":1493014,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"遲啲有冇機會見到中英合作對抗美國呢"}]}